Dialogue: 0,00:00:00.08,00:00:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever heard of coil?
Dialogue: 0,00:00:01.12,00:00:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just another online class.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:02.87,00:00:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a revolutionary way to connect students across the globe.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:06.00,00:00:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine working side by side with students from different countries,
Dialogue: 0,00:00:08.88,00:00:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,tackling shared projects and building trust, all while guided by
Dialogue: 0,00:00:12.32,00:00:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,expert educators.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:13.35,00:00:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,COIL stands for Collaborative Online International Learning, Blending virtual interactions
Dialogue: 0,00:00:17.76,00:00:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,with face to face sessions for a truly multicultural learning
Dialogue: 0,00:00:20.96,00:00:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,experience.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:21.76,00:00:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a lifeless MOOC or just a social media
Dialogue: 0,00:00:23.92,00:00:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,group.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:24.39,00:00:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's structured, engaging, and deeply collaborative.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:27.35,00:00:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Students and faculty work together to define goals, solve problems,
Dialogue: 0,00:00:30.71,00:00:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and share their insights.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:32.07,00:00:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,From icebreakers to final presentations, col builds connections that last.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:36.88,00:00:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you ready to step into a global classroom?
Dialogue: 0,00:00:38.92,00:00:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Check out the padlet, introduce yourself and join us on
Dialogue: 0,00:00:41.75,00:00:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,this incredible journey.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:43.03,00:00:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just education, it's transformation.
